This repository contains a modified Codex adaptation of the following upstream work:

  android-reverse-engineering-skill
  Author: Simone Avogadro
  Original target: Claude Code
  Source: https://github.com/SimoneAvogadro/android-reverse-engineering-skill

This repository changes the original work by:

- converting the Claude plugin layout to a Codex skill layout
- rewriting the skill entrypoint metadata for Codex
- adding Codex UI metadata in `agents/openai.yaml`
- removing Claude-only command and plugin files
- adding Codex-oriented installation and usage documentation
- adding a Windows PowerShell dependency installer for Codex users
